# Link to a wallet: Will bind your wallet-id to this discord. If on multiple discords, others don't have access to your possessed amount of eGLD
`egld$set <wallet_id>` or `egld$join <wallet_id>` or `egld$link <wallet_id>`

# Unlink a wallet: Will remove your wallet-id from the current discord
`egld$unset` or `egld$delete` or `egld$unlink`

# Display: Will show current value of eGLD or/and with your amount
`egld$value`
`egld$wallet`

# Server display: Will show all discord members' wallets
`egld$wallets`

# Link / Unlink all wallets accross all servers
`me$set <wallet_id>` or `me$join <wallet_id>` or `me$link <wallet_id>`
`me$delete` or `me$remove`

# Displays this :)
`egld$help`: utils.help,